{"tid":1468794,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[暫停捉鬼]其實支共提恐怖主義係個hint嚟","createTime":"2019-08-13T21:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:35.000Z","uid":26179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0db17e099060ae04e23f5e09a7af01dd7fb51a","tid":1468794,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:05:57.000Z","msg":"諗吓呢幾日有關鬼嘅行動<br />\n好可能想製造示威者無差別攻擊嘅形象<br />\n今日係捉到鬼<br />\n但第一冇咩實際成效<br />\n第二啲鬼明顯到係想你捉到咁<br />\n唔係話中計<br />\n但真係要諗吓有冇更深層嘅用意<br />\n<br />\n絕對有可能<br />\n搏緊你捉錯鬼<br />\n再話你無差別攻擊<br />\n咁就match咗恐怖主義<br />\n<br />\n就今日睇捉完鬼冇咩實質意義嚟講<br />\n暫停捉鬼先可以對抗到被恐怖主義去抹黑<br />\n雖然佢要點抹黑都阻唔到<br />\n但絕對冇必要畀口實佢咁做<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"b1f1cf97edeaf59d069709daeb72b89dab211904","tid":1468794,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:06:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"533a137a407ab0fc761b401e7a35064785d72549","tid":1468794,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:07:44.000Z","msg":"冇錯，宜家新疆都係以反恐嘅名義去實行北韓式統治"},{"pid":"615a8285c4bc34d2cde47844af6748cd72ca7c5a","tid":1468794,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"0d58ce9fdf35eeb72a2975d5a09e0b0b44aaa780","tid":1468794,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bc315234ab07135b309df8b9c582c4370f1af72","tid":1468794,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815ecb887a8e1ea1505b30982f0afdcb25ace873","tid":1468794,"uid":92340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"[警世]「不割蓆」可以走多遠？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1470878/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1470878/page/1</a>"}]}